      • currentQty

        public double currentQty
        Current quantity(in Pricing UOM). This is the quantity for which tax calculation is being done. This could be one of 1. line total quantity - when tax calculation is being done for the complete order line' 2. pre-settlement quantity - when tax calculation is being done for pre settlement 3. current invoice line quantity - when tax calculation is being done for an invoice line.

      • invoicedQty

        public double invoicedQty
        Invoiced quantity(in Pricing UOM). This is the quantity which has already been invoiced for the order line. This is passed only when this user exit is called for recalculating tax for an order line. It is not passed when called at invoicing.
